&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/CHICAGO-DOUBLE-A-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-8332&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/CHICAGO-DOUBLE-A-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;CHICAGO- DOUBLE A- OFFER- LOGO&quot; width=&quot;85&quot; height=&quot;75&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Double A is one of the more unique and exclusive lounges in Chicago. Entering through a heavy wood door with a peephole, the look and feel is definitely that of Chicago&rsquo;s Prohibition parlors of the past. Only 65 guests are able to experience the casual exclusivity of a bar program where creative drinks are made to order. Bottle Service specializes in tequila, with 75 different varieties as well as vodkas, gins, brandies, rums, whiskies and, of course, champagnes. Upscale casual attire.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please contact Double A by phone at +1 312-329-9555 or email at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:rsvp@doubleachicago.com&quot;&gt;rsvp@doubleachicago.com&lt;/a&gt; to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Nightlife Access to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to attend, number of guests, preferred time, cell phone or local (hotel) phone number and email address&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;For table service only, Double A requires a credit card at the time of booking to hold your reservation. You will be provided with pricing for the table you reserve. A credit card authorization form will be sent at the time of booking to be filled in and returned back.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cancellation policy for table service: Changes &amp;amp; cancellations must be made 3 hours in advance. If not cancelled 3 hours prior to the dining date or in the event of a no show, a fee in the amount of 50% of the agreed upon table/bottle price will be charged to your credit card.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconfirmation Policy: Please contact the nightclub by phone or email 24 hours prior to your arrival date to reconfirm. Provide a reminder that this is a Diners Club International Privileges Nightlife Access reservation. If not reconfirmed your reservation may be given away if need arises&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ages 21 &amp;amp; Over. ID must be provided.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Benefit is applicable for up to 4 guests in total.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bottle service required for tables after 22:00.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dress code will be strictly enforced. Management reserves the right to refuse entry to guests due to visible intoxication, lack of proper ID, failure to adhere to dress code, or capacity limits.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access is granted only with reservation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Late arrivals past midnight will be required to pay any required cover charges, despite having a reservation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Nightlife&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Diners Club Card must be used for payment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Nightlife Access benefit may not be combined with other offers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating&nbsp;Diners Club International&nbsp;Nightclub/Lounge merchant.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reservations&nbsp;based on availability at the time of booking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nightclub/lounge participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Blackout dates may apply due to event buyouts. Special event/DJs many incur a charge.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

